languages.text: "Я не вижу конвой, отправленный вам навстречу. Что случилось? Они не смогли вас найти и сопроводить? Если это так — поверьте, наказание будет суровым и стремительным".
"I'm not seeing the convoy I'd sent to meet you. What happened? Did they fail to find and escort you? If that is so, I promise you their punishment will be swift and severe."

languages.text: "Ich sehe den Konvoi nicht, den ich ausgeschickt habe, Euch zu empfangen. Was ist passiert? Haben sie Euch denn nicht gefunden und eskortiert? Wenn dem so ist, so verspreche ich, sie schnell und streng zu bestrafen."

languages.text: « Je ne vois pas le convoi que j'avais envoyé à votre rencontre. Que s'est-il passé ? Ils devaient vous escorter, ont-ils manqué à leur devoir ? Si c'est le cas, je vous assure que leur châtiment sera prompt et sévère. »
languages.original_text: "I'm not seeing the convoy I'd sent to meet you. What happened? Did they fail to find and escort you? If that is so, I promise you their punishment will be swift and severe."

languages.text: “我并没有看到我派去接应您的护卫队，这是发生了什么事情？他们是没找到您，没能护送您前来此地吗？如果真是这样，我向您保证，他们很快就会受到严厉的惩罚。”
languages.original_text: "I'm not seeing the convoy I'd sent to meet you. What happened? Did they fail to find and escort you? If that is so, I promise you their punishment will be swift and severe."

languages.text: 「あなたに会うために送った護送が見えないな。何が起きた？あなたを発見できず護衛に失敗したと？そうだとしたら、ただちに彼らに厳しい罰を与えると約束しよう」
languages.original_text: "I'm not seeing the convoy I'd sent to meet you. What happened? Did they fail to find and escort you? If that is so, I promise you their punishment will be swift and severe."

languages.text: «No veo el convoy que había enviado a su encuentro. ¿Qué ha ocurrido aquí? ¿No le han encontrado y escoltado? Si es así, te prometo que su castigo será rápido y severo».
languages.original_text: "I'm not seeing the convoy I'd sent to meet you. What happened? Did they fail to find and escort you? If that is so, I promise you their punishment will be swift and severe."

languages.text: "Sizi karşılaması için gönderdiğim konvoyu göremiyorum. Ne oldu? Sizi bulup eşlik etmeyi başaramadılar mı? Durum buysa sözüm olsun, cezaları tez ve ağır olacaktır."
